  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "🔥 Sales & Team Building Executive",
  "description": "<p>🚀 Build Results. Build People. Build Your Career.</p><p>Are you hungry for success, enjoy working with people, and want more than just a “job”?<br />We’re looking for <strong>driven individuals</strong> who want to <strong>excel in sales</strong> and <strong>grow into leadership & team-building roles</strong>.</p><h3>💼 What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li><p>Represent well-known brands through <strong>events, roadshows & face-to-face sales</strong></p></li><li><p>Drive sales performance and hit personal targets</p></li><li><p>Learn how to <strong>recruit, train & lead a high-performing team</strong></p></li><li><p>Develop leadership, communication & people-management skills</p></li></ul><h3>💎 What You’ll Get</h3><ul><li><p>💰 <strong>Uncapped earnings</strong> (performance-based)</p></li><li><p>📈 <strong>Clear career progression</strong> into leadership & management</p></li><li><p>🤝 <strong>1-to-1 mentorship</strong> from experienced leaders</p></li><li><p>🌍 Exposure to real-world sales & business operations</p></li><li><p>🔥 Energetic, supportive, and growth-driven team culture</p></li></ul><h3>🎯 Who We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Self-motivated, ambitious, and results-driven</p></li><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people</p></li><li><p>Open to learning sales, leadership & team building</p></li><li><p>No experience needed – <strong>attitude & hunger matter most</strong></p></li></ul><p>If you’re ready to <strong>earn what you’re worth</strong>, grow fast, and build something bigger than yourself —<br />👉 <strong>Apply now and start your journey with us.</strong></p>",
